      <title>博客搭建工具Hexo的相关配置</title>
      <link href="/2019/06/29/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7Hexo%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
      <url>/2019/06/29/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7Hexo%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>之前一直觉得写博客没有必要，后来突然心血来潮想搞个博客来玩玩。等搞好了之后，感觉还是不错的。中间踩了很多坑，下面会一一讲到。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h2><h3 id="注册Github-账号"><a href="#注册Github-账号" class="headerlink" title="注册Github 账号"></a>注册Github 账号</h3><p>跳过了，之后有时间再写。</p><h3 id="下载安装Git-Node-js"><a href="#下载安装Git-Node-js" class="headerlink" title="下载安装Git, Node.js"></a>下载安装Git, Node.js</h3><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git官网</a></p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Node.js官网</a></p><p>至于为什么要安装这些工具呢，因为这是后面用到的Hexo的依赖啊。</p><h3 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h3><p>npm install hexo-cli -g  </p><p>后面的之后在写吧！</p><p>这目前只是一个测试的文件</p><p>第二次测</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>0123456789</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"I am testing the editor"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">表头一</th><th align="left">表头二</th><th align="left">表头三</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">刘备</td><td align="left">哭</td><td align="left">大个</td></tr><tr><td align="left">关羽</td><td align="left">打</td><td align="left">二哥</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;a);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, a);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>hello</strong></p><p><strong><em>hello</em></strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
